<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">

<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Document</title>
</head>

<body>

    <style>
        body {
            background: black;
        }

        h1 {
            text-align: center;
            color: orange;
        }

        .buttons {
            text-align: center;
        }

        .button {
            text-align: center;
            text-decoration: none;
            display: inline-block;

        }

        .button1 {
            background-color: white;
            border-radius: 4px;
            color: black;
            border: 2px solid orange;
            display: inline-block;
            border: none;
            color: black;
            padding: 16px 32px;
            text-decoration: none;
            font-size: 16px;
            margin: 4px 2px;
            transition-duration: 0.4s;
            cursor: pointer;
        }

        .button1:hover {
            background-color: orange;
            color: white;
        }

        .button2 {
            background-color: white;
            border-radius: 4px;
            color: black;
            border: 2px solid orange;
            display: inline-block;
            border: none;
            color: black;
            padding: 16px 32px;
            text-decoration: none;
            font-size: 16px;
            margin: 10px 10px;
            transition-duration: 0.4s;
            cursor: pointer;
        }

        .button2:hover {
            background-color: orange;
            color: white;
        }

        h3,
        p {
            color: papayawhip;
            font-size: large;
            border: 20%;
        }

        #footer {
            margin-left: 40%;
            position: absolute;
            bottom: 0;
            width: 100%;
            height: 2.5rem;
            /* Footer height */
        }

        #card {
            margin-left: 7%;
        }

        #h3 {
            margin-left: 3%;
            padding: 1%;
        }
    </style>

    <h1>NEWS THAT MATTERS</h1>
    <hr>
    <div class="buttons">
        <form class="button" action="/news" method="post">
            <button class="button1"><b>Trending News</b></button>
        </form>
        <form class="button" action="/googletrendsdata" method="post">
            <button class="button2"><b>Popular Searches</b> </button>
        </form>
    </div>
    <div class="about">
        <h3> <u id="h3"> HOW IT WORKS..</u></h3>
        <div id="card">
            <p>First we collect the most popular searches of that day by using google trends api <br>

                then we curate news articles related to those popular searches.<br>

                finally the headline and a few lines regarrding that news is provided along with a link that takes you
                to
                the original news article.
            </p>
        </div>
    </div>

    <div id="footer">

        <p>made with ❤️ by <a href="https://github.com/BalaMithran">mithran bala</p></a>
    </div id="footer">


</body>

</html>